!! Discovery filter

```
[plugin-type[plugin]prefix[$:/plugins/rimir/]!title[$:/plugins/rimir/core-hook]sort[name]]
```

Finds all installed rimir plugins except core-hook itself.

!! State tiddler

|!Tiddler |!Purpose |
|`$:/state/rimir/core-hook/selected` |Currently selected plugin title in the sidebar |

!! Convention: settings tiddler

|!Pattern |!Purpose |
|`$:/plugins/rimir/<slug>/settings` |Settings panel content — transcluded by the hub and shown in plugin detail view |

!! Convention: icon tiddler

|!Pattern |!Purpose |
|`$:/plugins/rimir/<slug>/icon` |SVG icon displayed in the sidebar and header (16pt sidebar, 28pt header) |

!! CSS classes (from theme plugin)

|!Class |!Purpose |
|`rr-settings-hub` |Top-level flex container (sidebar + content) |
|`rr-settings-sidebar` |Left sidebar with plugin list |
|`rr-settings-plugin-item` |Clickable button for each plugin |
|`rr-settings-plugin-active` |Highlighted state (accent left border) |
|`rr-settings-plugin-name` |Plugin name text (truncated) |
|`rr-settings-plugin-version` |Version badge (muted) |
|`rr-settings-content` |Right content area |
|`rr-settings-header` |Plugin header with icon + name + description |
|`rr-settings-info-card` |Dashed fallback card for plugins without settings |

</$fill>
</$transclude>
